WORK IN PROGRESS NOT YET READY FOR PRODUCTION

  This is a simple gem that will allow for easy to use authentication system
for rails 3 applications using Datamapper. 

  Simple builds the necessary tables and controllers to handle all of your 
authentication needs including email verification, user login and logout, 
and password reset. 

  Installing and using this authentication system only requires 3 simple steps
  
  1) Add the following line to your gemfile:
        gem "easy-auth"
  2) $ bundle install
  3) $ rails generate easy-auth:install
